					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was hesitant to add more to the addendum because it's effectively a punchline, and I thought dragging it out would diminish the effect. Maybe I could have added more buildup, but I wasn't convinced that the anomaly was interesting enough that I could lengthen the article without losing readers' interest.</p> <p>Anyways, I appreciate the feedback.</p> 
				 	]]>
